 <!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
	<meta charset="UTF-8">
	<title>{{title}}</title>
	<meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
</head>

<body>
	<div class="content">
        {{{header}}}
		<!--导航栏-->
        {{{mainnav}}}
		<div class="interactive_con">
			<div class="con content80">
				<div class="remind">
					<span id="close" class="close"></span>
					<img src="../../common/images/portal/suona.png" alt="" /> 温馨提示：在这里，您可以对泸州市政务大厅服务、办事事项等进行咨询，我们会通过您预留的方式尽快回复您。同时，建议您不要就同一问题反复咨询。
				</div>
				<div class="suggest_con">
					<dl class="clearfix">
						<dt>
							<img src="../../common/images/portal/star.png" alt="" />建议类别</dt>
						<dd class="suggest_type downselect-wrap">
							<span class="downselect-btn"></span>
							<input type="text" id="suggest_type" class="downselect-inpu" readonly="readonly" value="请选择" />
							<ul id="type_list" class="downselect-selectwrap">
							</ul>
						</dd>
					</dl>
					<dl class="clearfix">
						<dt>
							<img src="../../common/images/portal/star.png" alt="" />建议标题</dt>
						<dd class="suggest_title">
							<input type="text" id="suggest_title" class="title_" autocomplete="off" name="appraise_cont" placeholder="请填写少于30个字">
						</dd>
					</dl>
					<dl class="clearfix">
						<dt>
							<img src="../../common/images/portal/star.png" alt="" />建议内容</dt>
						<dd class="suggest_cont">
							<div>
								<textarea id="suggest_txt" name="appraise_cont" autocomplete="off" placeholder="若您对我们的服务不满意或非常不满意时，请您填写不满意的具体内容，以便我们改善服务质量。" rows="6" cols="95"></textarea>
								<a class="words_num">
									<span id="words_current">0</span>/500</a>
							</div>
						</dd>
					</dl>
					<dl class="clearfix">
						<dt>
							<img src="../../common/images/portal/star.png" alt="" />是否公开</dt>
						<dd class="suggest_public">
							<label for="yes">
								<input type="radio" name="yn" id="yes" checked="checked"/>
								<span class="radio"></span>是</label>
							<label for="no">
								<input type="radio" name="yn" id="no" />
								<span class="radio"></span>否</label>
						</dd>
					</dl>
					<dl class="clearfix">
						<dt>上传图片</dt>
						<dd id="push_img">
							<div class="img_wrap"></div>
							<div class="add">
								<label for="push">
									<input id="push" type="file"  />
									<img src="../../common/images/portal/select.png" alt="" />
								</label>
							</div>
						</dd>
					</dl>
					<dl class="btn_wrap clearfix">
						<dt>&nbsp;</dt>
						<dd>
							<a href="" id="sub">提交</a>
							<a href="javascript:history.back(-1)" id="return">取消</a>
						</dd>
					</dl>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		{{{footer}}}
	</div>
</body>

</html>